Pegasystems - Wikipedia






















 






Pegasystems

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Pegasystems Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: PEGA[1]


Industry
Software


Founded
1983


Headquarters
Cambridge, Massachusetts, United States



Number of locations

35 (2017)[2]



